history.content:
Has the enrollment cap for the graduate section of this class been reduced?

I remember when I initially signed up for the course during my Phase 1, I was high enough on the waitlist that there were more open spots than that. When I last checked today (not sure how long it's been like this), I noticed that enrollment was completely full and that I'd barely moved up 10 spots. I don't remember how many total seats there were before but it definitely feels like the section has gotten much smaller. Is there any possibility of expansion, especially considering how much larger the 194 section is?
